gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 127, Timberwolves 120
gameRecap.excerpt: The Celtics defeated the Timberwolves, 127-120 in OT. Jayson Tatum recorded a game-high 45 points along with four rebounds and two assists for the Celtics, with Jaylen Brown adding 35 points and 11 rebounds in the victory. Anthony Edwards tallied 29 points, six rebounds, and three assists for the Timberwolves in the losing effort. The Celtics are now 18-0 at home this season and improve to 29-8 in the regular season, while the Timberwolves fall to 26-11.
